	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Personally I love big MMC1 games with more than 256kb of ROM or more than 8kb of VRAM (SUROM, SOROM, SXROM) tough I don't have any.
<br />
<br />They beat the MMC3 because you can support more SRAM, more PRG bankswitching shemes, 1-screen mirroring and have CHRRAM (well MMC3 can also have CHRRAM and 1-screen mirroring but those carts are rare and you need to modify more common carts to get them).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


